🔹 🎯 Task: Closest Number to Target (use Math class function at least one)

📥 Inputs:
int a;
int b;
int target;

⚙️ Requirements:
Determine which number (a or b) is closer to target
Print:
"A is closer"
"B is closer"
"Both are equally close"

📤 Example:
a = 8
b = 12
target = 10

Output: Both are equally close